description:
W°n✝∀ is part of "kisetsu". 
This digital painting plays with shapes and patterns. 
Winter is symbol of silence and self-consciousness, solitude and detachment. 
The Death. 
This Vortex called Life comes to an end. But don’t despair. Winter ushers in Spring, and the cycle of life starts again bringing a message of hope and rebirth. 
 What I see is not what everyone sees, look inside yourself, find the meaning.
